<h1 id="sleep">Sleep</h1>
<p>In some areas of modern society, sleep has become viewed as a luxury which can be sacrificed to some degree, in order to provide time to accomplish more. What this view misses is that sleep is an essential and active process that maintains mental, physical, and cognitive health. Sacrificing sleep on a regular basis may therefore lead to less productivity and more health issues in the long term.</p>

<h2 id="recommendations">Recommendations</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Get the recommended quantity of sleep, which for most people is 7-9 hours</li>
  <li>Try to get high quality sleep by following a healthy circadian rhythm</li>
</ul>

