<h1 id="closing-comments">Closing comments</h1>
<p>One thing this examination of principles for physical health lacks is a discussion of the role of mental health. This is important to consider as mental well-being, or lack thereof, can have a large impact on physical health.</p>

<p>This list is not exhaustive or perfect, if you find any inaccuracy or know of anything important that this list lacks please let me know!</p>
